- !!! INSTRUCTIONS !!! -  

The camera connects by CSI
The Display connects by DSI
The botton enters by GPIO configurated with the intern pull up 
The termic printer conects by a serial TTL
The alimentation has to be estable and separated by roots if necesary 


--------

clone the repositor and instal dependences
(pip install -r requierment.txt)

conecct hardware and verify that the serial puerto of the printer its oki
anddd let the rpogramm go

power on the sistem and wait for the raspberi to start, press the push botton and the sistem will get the photo,
it will show it to u and print it!

