NOTES !!

THE GPIO OF RASPBERRY PI WORK ON 3.3 V
DO NOT CONNECT 5V SEGNALS DIRECT TO GPIO
THE TERMIC PRINTER HAS TO HAVE AN ESTABLE ALIMENTATION
I RECOMMED TO USE SEPARATED NAMES OF THE MODULES AND ARCHIVES TO MAKE IT CLEAN


